content: I'm a graphic designer with decades of experience, and I'd like to put my talents to work creating graphics for the Reach galleries. Who can I talk to?

Hi <@337277887038357507> so great to see you here wanting to use your graphic talents to move this forward to a win. You can apply to Content Brigade with this form https://forms.gle/KypguusgSb1YWJQG7
While you are waiting to hear from content brigade, take a look around and choose an engagement training that supports you to connect with voters.
